ia producing  million tons per year it participates in a uranium mine development in cigar lake mine in canada idemitsu is working on geothermal power in ōita prefecture japan the plant will use a binary power generation system that produces electricity from both the steam with a regular turbine and from hot water by vaporizing pentane which then drives a turbine together with mitsubishi corporation idemitsu plans to massproduce biofuel from non food crops using a method developed by honda and the research institute of innovative technology for the earth for converting rice straw and weeds to ethanol fuel the factory will likely be placed in north america china or southeast asia where the raw materials are available for a low price advertisement and sponsorshipedit idemitsu museum of arts two art museums in tokyo and moji where idemitsu  co was started idemitsu music prize   idemitsu ihatove trial イーハトーブトライアル  a motorcycle trial ultra idemitsujin ultraman characters used in tv commercials referencesedit  a b company profile  idemitsu kosan idemitsu official website archived from the original on  retrieved    a b global   idemitsu kosan fortune global  fortune magazine july   retrieved    stock quote bloomberg retrieved    a b yamanaka megumi october   idemitsu raises  billion yen in oil refiner ipo bloomberg lp retrieved    global   industry petroleum refining fortune global  fortune magazine july   retrieved    topix new index series as of october   tokyo stock exchange  nikkei  constituents nikkei retrieved    a b c d e f g h i j international directory of company histories vol  st james press  as quoted on answerscom article retrieved   and fundinguniverse retrieved    a b c d e f idemitsu kōsan co ltd  in encyclopædia britannica retrieved november   from encyclopædia britannica online  again the rising sun time magazine july   retrieved    japan to resume export of russian oil russian economic news via europe intelligence wire  october  retrieved    new iphone s