inue trying to win over founding family july    am jst japans idemitsu to proceed with share sale after court rejects family petition july    pm jst japan court rejects idemitsu family petition to block share sale july    pm jst japans corporate governance gets some longoverdue scrutiny encouraged by new codes institutional investors turn up the heat on management july    am jst japans corporate governance gets some longoverdue scrutiny encouraged by new codes institutional investors turn up the heat on management july    am jst idemitsu stock plunges  on plan to issue new shares july    am jst more news for idemitsu kosan co ltd financial highlights mar  local currency us dollar revenue b gross profit m operating income m income before tax m net income m ebitda m diluted eps  dividends per share  total assets b total liabilities b total equity m operating cash flow m currency in jpy historical data revenue m gross profit m operating income m income before tax m net income m ebitda m diluted eps  dividends per share  total assets m total liabilities m total equity m operating cash flow m currency in usd historical data valuation measures mar  per  roa  roe  operating margin  profit margin  key executive president chief executive officer  director takashi tsukioka representative director  vice president yoshihisa matsumoto representative director  vice president daisuke seki executive officer  managersales yuji arai executive officer sakugoro matsuda share holders nissho kosan kk idemitsu bunka fukushi zaidan idemitsu museum of arts mitsubishi ufj financial group inc idemitsu kosan employee stock ownership plan sumitomo mitsui financial group inc sumitomo mitsui trust holdings inc idemitsu makasazu idemitsu masamichi the vanguard group inc show more show fewer address website httpwwwidemitsucojp address  marunouchi chiyodaku tokyo  japan phone  help copyright   factset research systems inc all rights reserved related companies idemitsu canada corp idemitsu oil develo